jm.midi.event

Interface SysComEvt

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Event
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SysEx

    public interface SysComEvt
extends Event
    Provides an interface for System Common Events. System Common events will usually be placed into an Event List in which they will be classed as Event Types. SysComEvt extends the Event interface.
